---
layout: base.njk
current: educators
permalink: /educators/
title: For Educators
description: "Sounds of Saving brings a music-based, SEL-rooted mental health curriculum to high schools and college campuses. Now accepting pilot partners for the 2026 to 2027 school year."
ogType: website
---
{#
  For Educators — dedicated landing page for school counselors, SEL leads, and
  college wellness staff. Thesis headline, two curriculum tracks + a workshop
  band (each a "what you get" spec list + one CTA), a proof band, a lead-magnet
  pointer to the white paper, and a STUBBED intake form. Copy is CMS-editable
  via content/pages/educators.json.

  FORM IS A STUB: action="#", no backend yet. Before launch it must be wired to
  Netlify Forms (add `data-netlify="true"` + a hidden form-name input, or a
  /forms POST) with the submission routed to a shared programs@ alias, never a
  personal inbox. See the comment block on the <form> below.
#}
{% set e = pages.educators %}

<style>
  .edu-page { padding-block: var(--space-xl); }
  .edu-page h1 {
    font-size: var(--fs-mega);
    line-height: var(--lh-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    max-width: 16ch;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }
  .edu-lead { font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: var(--lh-base); max-width: var(--maxw-prose); margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg); }

  .edu-pullquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
    max-width: var(--maxw-prose);
  }
  .edu-pullquote blockquote { font-family: var(--font-body); font-style: italic; font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: var(--lh-base); margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs); max-width: none; }
  .edu-pullquote cite { font-style: normal; font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--text-muted); }
  .edu-why { max-width: var(--maxw-prose); line-height: var(--lh-base); margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xl); }

  .edu-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    color: var(--coral);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs);
  }

  /* track grid */
  .tracks { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .tracks__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .track {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--paper-2);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .track__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs);
  }
  .track__title { font-size: var(--fs-h3); margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs); }
  .track__summary { font-size: var(--fs-small); line-height: var(--lh-base); margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm); }
  .track__audience { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 0 var(--space-md); }
  .track__audience strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .track__spec-h {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs);
  }
  .track__spec { margin: 0 0 var(--space-md); padding-left: var(--space-md); }
  .track__spec li { font-size: var(--fs-small); line-height: var(--lh-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2xs); }
  .track__cta { margin-top: auto; }

  /* proof band */
  .proof-band {
    background: var(--dusk);
    color: var(--on-dark);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  .proof-band h2 { color: var(--on-dark); font-size: var(--fs-h2); max-width: 24ch; margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg); }
  .proof-band .edu-eyebrow { color: var(--coral); }
  .proof-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .proof-stat__num { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h2); color: var(--coral); line-height: 1; margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs); }
  .proof-stat__body { font-size: var(--fs-small); line-height: var(--lh-base); color: var(--paper-2); margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs); max-width: none; }
  .proof-stat__src { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-tiny); color: var(--ink-faint); }
  .proof-band .proof-stat__src { color: var(--line); }
  .proof-cred { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--dusk-2); padding-top: var(--space-lg); }
  .proof-cred li { font-size: var(--fs-small); line-height: var(--lh-base); color: var(--paper-2); margin-bottom: var(--space-2xs); padding-left: var(--space-md); position: relative; }
  .proof-cred li::before { content: "+"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--coral); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

  /* lead magnet */
  .lead-magnet {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--paper-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  .lead-magnet__copy { max-width: var(--maxw-prose); }
  .lead-magnet h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h3); margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs); }
  .lead-magnet p { font-size: var(--fs-small); line-height: var(--lh-base); margin: 0; }

  /* intake form */
  .intake { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: var(--space-xl); }
  .intake__head { max-width: var(--maxw-prose); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .intake h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h2); margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs); }
  .intake__head p { line-height: var(--lh-base); margin: 0; }
  .intake-form {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: var(--maxw-prose);
  }
  .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3xs); }
  .field--full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .field label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }
  .field input,
  .field select,
  .field textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-base);
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-2xs) var(--space-xs);
  }
  .field textarea { min-height: 7rem; resize: vertical; }
  .field input:focus,
  .field select:focus,
  .field textarea:focus { outline: 2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset: 1px; }
  .intake__submit { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .intake__note { grid-column: 1 / -1; font-size: var(--fs-tiny); color: var(--text-faint); margin: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .intake-form { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<div class="container edu-page">
  <h1>{{ e.heading }}</h1>
  {% if e.lead %}<p class="edu-lead">{{ e.lead }}</p>{% endif %}

  {% if e.pullquote %}
  <figure class="edu-pullquote">
    <blockquote>{{ e.pullquote }}</blockquote>
    {% if e.pullquote_attribution %}<cite>{{ e.pullquote_attribution }}</cite>{% endif %}
  </figure>
  {% endif %}

  {% if e.why_music %}<p class="edu-why">{{ e.why_music }}</p>{% endif %}

  {# — Two tracks + workshop band ————————————————————————————————— #}
  <section class="tracks" aria-label="Programs for educators">
    <ul class="tracks__grid">
      {% for t in e.tracks %}
      <li class="track">
        {% if t.eyebrow %}<p class="track__eyebrow">{{ t.eyebrow }}</p>{% endif %}
        <h2 class="track__title">{{ t.title }}</h2>
        {% if t.summary %}<p class="track__summary">{{ t.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if t.audience %}<p class="track__audience"><strong>For:</strong> {{ t.audience }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if t.spec.length %}
        <p class="track__spec-h">{{ t.spec_heading or "What you get" }}</p>
        <ul class="track__spec">
          {% for s in t.spec %}<li>{{ s }}</li>{% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}
        {% if t.cta %}
        <p class="track__cta"><a class="btn btn--primary" href="{{ t.cta.href }}">{{ t.cta.label }}</a></p>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  {# — Proof band ————————————————————————————————————————————————— #}
  {% if e.proof %}
  <section class="proof-band" aria-label="{{ e.proof.eyebrow or 'Why now' }}">
    {% if e.proof.eyebrow %}<p class="edu-eyebrow">{{ e.proof.eyebrow }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if e.proof.heading %}<h2>{{ e.proof.heading }}</h2>{% endif %}
    {% if e.proof.stats.length %}
    <ul class="proof-stats">
      {% for s in e.proof.stats %}
      <li class="proof-stat">
        <p class="proof-stat__num">{{ s.stat }}</p>
        <p class="proof-stat__body">{{ s.body }}</p>
        {% if s.source %}<p class="proof-stat__src">{{ s.source }}</p>{% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
    {% if e.proof.credibility.length %}
    <ul class="proof-cred">
      {% for c in e.proof.credibility %}<li>{{ c }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {# — Lead magnet (white paper) ——————————————————————————————————— #}
  {% if e.lead_magnet %}
  <aside class="lead-magnet" aria-label="{{ e.lead_magnet.title }}">
    <div class="lead-magnet__copy">
      {% if e.lead_magnet.eyebrow %}<p class="edu-eyebrow">{{ e.lead_magnet.eyebrow }}</p>{% endif %}
      <h2>{{ e.lead_magnet.title }}</h2>
      <p>{{ e.lead_magnet.body }}</p>
    </div>
    {% if e.lead_magnet.cta %}
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ e.lead_magnet.cta.href }}">{{ e.lead_magnet.cta.label }}</a>
    {% endif %}
  </aside>
  {% endif %}

  {# — Intake form (STUB) ————————————————————————————————————————— #}
  {% if e.intake %}
  <section class="intake" id="intake" aria-label="{{ e.intake.heading }}">
    <div class="intake__head">
      {% if e.intake.eyebrow %}<p class="edu-eyebrow">{{ e.intake.eyebrow }}</p>{% endif %}
      <h2>{{ e.intake.heading }}</h2>
      {% if e.intake.body %}<p>{{ e.intake.body }}</p>{% endif %}
    </div>

    {# Submits via the visitor's email client (mailto). Swap for a hosted form
       endpoint (Formspree / a serverless handler) routed to a shared programs@
       alias if a backend is added later. #}
    <form class="intake-form" id="intake-form">
      <div class="field">
        <label for="f-name">Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="f-name" name="name" autocomplete="name">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="f-role">Role</label>
        <input type="text" id="f-role" name="role" placeholder="Counselor, SEL lead, wellness staff" autocomplete="organization-title">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="f-school">School or institution</label>
        <input type="text" id="f-school" name="school" autocomplete="organization">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="f-email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="f-email" name="email" autocomplete="email">
      </div>
      <div class="field field--full">
        <label for="f-track">Which track</label>
        <select id="f-track" name="track">
          <option value="">No preference yet</option>
          <option value="sos-hs">SoS HS (high school)</option>
          <option value="sos-uni">SoS Uni (college)</option>
          <option value="workshop">Bring an Artist Workshop</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field field--full">
        <label for="f-message">Message</label>
        <textarea id="f-message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us about your school and what you're hoping for."></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="intake__submit">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Request a pilot conversation</button>
      </div>
    </form>
    <script>
      (function () {
        var f = document.getElementById("intake-form");
        if (!f) return;
        var val = function (id) { var el = document.getElementById(id); return el ? el.value.trim() : ""; };
        f.addEventListener("submit", function (e) {
          e.preventDefault();
          var subject = "Educator inquiry" + (val("f-track") ? " (" + val("f-track") + ")" : "");
          var body = [
            "Name: " + val("f-name"),
            "Role: " + val("f-role"),
            "School or institution: " + val("f-school"),
            "Email: " + val("f-email"),
            "Track: " + val("f-track"),
            "",
            val("f-message")
          ].join("\n");
          window.location.href = "mailto:programs@soundsofsaving.org?subject=" +
            encodeURIComponent(subject) + "&body=" + encodeURIComponent(body);
        });
      })();
    </script>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
</div>
